Every new change is resulting in production defects due to insufficient knowledge about the application, impacting other products and business operations.
Extended testing times and production issues are negatively affecting client business.
The deployment process is delayed and complicated due to manual and semi-automated methods.
The time taken to resolve production incidents is increased because of the lack of domain knowledge among L2 and L3 support teams.
The support team frequently has to consult the development team for assistance, which impacts development time for delivering new features.
